window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Penny never had a structured life growing up, so she has lived her whole adulthood according to her life goals and plans. She makes decisions based on thought-out reasoning, and she never ventures out of her comfort zone. </p> <p>All of that changes when she meets Jeremy. Jeremy is rebellious and wild but makes her feel free. She begins to fall for him before finding out that he is a billionaire rock star. Penny is introduced to a new way of living. The two of them are opposite and lead totally different lives, but they just might be exactly what the other needs. </p> <p>Will Penny find her happiness outside of her life plans, or will going off route set her up for a tragic disaster? </p>"; 
